OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry with a mix of sunshine and cloudy
OL,7,Fperiods. Chance of isolated thundery
OL,8,Fshowers at times, mainly affecting
OL,9,Fhills. Freshening easterly winds by
OL,10,FSunday. Temperatures above average
OL,11,Fthroughout.
